Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.90,0:00:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐  把衣服脱掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.28,0:00:13.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会帮你  脱的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.24,0:00:19.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么  等…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.29,0:00:21.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手啊  美羽
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.87,0:00:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮啊  姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.17,0:00:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是太漂亮了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.26,0:00:33.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.77,0:00:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.23,0:00:44.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.60,0:00:45.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是新婚旅行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.10,0:00:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,必须打扮得漂漂亮亮的才行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.99,0:00:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来  空
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.53,0:01:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然办不成婚礼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.83,0:01:03.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但这是我用三个月的打工钱买的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.80,0:01:14.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.92,0:01:18.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,与这些相比  还是空更漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.74,0:01:36.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小空
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.32,0:01:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帮我撒点露娜露娜7拌料
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.96,0:03:19.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\fs24\b1\3c&H18EB66&\pos(137,255)}欲见君时君不在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.85,0:03:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个刚炸好的  很美味哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.23,0:03:30.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还不错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.52,0:03:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那给我些炸奶酪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.23,0:03:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要十个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.23,0:03:36.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.61,0:03:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天小雏去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.99,0:03:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天美羽去接她
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.45,0:03:42.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.86,0:03:44.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那把这些可乐饼带给小雏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.37,0:03:46.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  总是受您照顾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.37,0:03:48.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小雏的姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.29,0:03:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小雏不在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.08,0:03:53.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.37,0:03:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  小雏今天去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.04,0:03:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊  今天是美羽…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.22,0:04:02.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这真让人吃惊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.18,0:04:05.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小雏的人气好高
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.30,0:04:07.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.97,0:04:09.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祐太也说过
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.47,0:04:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们好像把小雏视如己女了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.69,0:04:16.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说到哥哥  他在学校是什么样子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.48,0:04:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沉睡之人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.78,0:04:20.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沉睡之人？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.11,0:04:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  反正传闻说他总是在上课时暴睡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.32,0:04:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以说是沉睡之人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.37,0:04:30.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然打工打过头了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.29,0:04:33.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但还是要打起精神  因为是爸爸嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.50,0:04:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祐太说过的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.75,0:04:41.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么困难的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.01,0:04:46.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样子估计也不能来路研了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.76,0:04:47.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.43,0:04:51.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过现在这种做爸爸的感觉还不错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.68,0:04:54.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,工作之后回到家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.77,0:04:56.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看到孩子们的脸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.02,0:04:59.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感觉非常的幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.32,0:05:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥说过这些话？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.48,0:05:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  所以我说想成为妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.66,0:05:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为你们三人实在是可爱得不行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.75,0:05:17.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.21,0:05:25.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦  我怎么…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.18,0:05:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胸部变大了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.39,0:05:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.68,0:05:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.18,0:05:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.27,0:05:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.56,0:05:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,慢走  哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.57,0:05:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂  什么哥哥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.65,0:05:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们都结婚了  该怎么称呼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.74,0:05:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.08,0:05:53.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祐…祐太
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.46,0:05:58.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那来个临别之吻
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.37,0:05:59.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.88,0:06:08.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,终于清醒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.47,0:06:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你最近怎么总是睡觉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.55,0:06:13.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.51,0:06:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.85,0:06:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我最近也总这样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.27,0:06:20.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这上下学的路程真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.61,0:06:23.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎  如果能坐的话还好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.78,0:06:27.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可早上时基本都是一路站着的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.44,0:06:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么叫一路站着？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.61,0:06:32.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊  舅舅回来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.12,0:06:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.37,0:06:36.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回家  舅舅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.16,0:06:38.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回家
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.66,0:06:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天乖不乖啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.12,0:06:43.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我学会翻单杠了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.46,0:06:45.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  小雏真厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.05,0:06:47.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我马上就写完了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.13,0:06:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们先去洗澡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.34,0:06:51.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.59,0:06:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那小雏  要洗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.35,0:06:54.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  要的要的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.93,0:06:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我找找  替换衣服在…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.36,0:07:05.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么说呢  那个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.53,0:07:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,房间里太那个了是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.65,0:07:09.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.78,0:07:12.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新学期一忙就没有注意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.03,0:07:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用不着道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.57,0:07:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也忙得团团转啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.49,0:07:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,生活就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.25,0:07:22.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Twinkle twinkle
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.71,0:07:25.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊  脱太早啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.29,0:07:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在练习表演哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.00,0:07:28.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊  原来是在练习啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.09,0:07:30.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好  朝浴室go吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.13,0:07:32.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go Go
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.05,0:07:35.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go Go
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.66,0:07:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,带来了哦  我的丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.95,0:07:58.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦  好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.37,0:08:00.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.87,0:08:02.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的  空
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.00,0:08:05.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用见面我们也知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.50,0:08:06.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.29,0:08:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祐太他忘了东西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.55,0:08:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子很粗心大意的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.63,0:08:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,忘了东西？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.64,0:08:17.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去帮他一起去找吧  空
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.87,0:08:41.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs12\bord2\shad0}夏日的问候、各位过的怎么样。\N这次是因为小鸟游 信吾、祐理的坟建好了\N故此与你们联系\N近期如果能顺便过来看看的话、我想他们也会高兴的吧。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.32,0:08:47.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是果然还是去不了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.04,0:08:51.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还要去接小雏和做晚饭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.34,0:08:54.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起了  爸爸  祐理小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.72,0:08:58.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上学情况如何  累吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.93,0:09:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.35,0:09:02.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,社团活动开心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.35,0:09:07.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  很开心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.06,0:09:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.61,0:09:12.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐也很高兴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.19,0:09:14.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小空进了社团
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.95,0:09:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟大家一起快乐地相处了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.11,0:09:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祐理姐说的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.12,0:09:20.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.24,0:09:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然还会发生很多麻烦事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.20,0:09:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过一定要努力到毕业哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.12,0:09:27.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瞧我  是不是太把自己当父亲了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.96,0:09:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂  美羽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.76,0:09:35.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚才不是叫你擦下桌子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.55,0:09:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好困
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.30,0:09:41.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是偷偷打游戏到很晚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.06,0:09:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才不是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.81,0:09:44.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.60,0:09:47.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没说错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.90,0:09:51.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.94,0:09:54.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然是跟你这么长时间呆在一起了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.53,0:09:55.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,切~
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.61,0:09:57.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了  小雏  起来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.99,0:10:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂  起来了  小雏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.45,0:10:05.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  再让我睡会儿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.91,0:10:06.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.00,0:10:08.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.33,0:10:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前段时间给你的药  带着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.84,0:10:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.71,0:10:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,实在不行就吃点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.01,0:10:16.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要吃太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.92,0:10:18.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,实在不行的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.59,0:10:19.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.26,0:10:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早上很努力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.18,0:10:26.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要让舅舅太担心为好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.27,0:10:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.94,0:10:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再继续这样为难哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.61,0:10:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绝对会出问题
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.65,0:10:35.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,船到桥头自然直嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.86,0:10:38.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要大家一起齐心协力的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.40,0:11:13.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.98,0:11:17.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莱…莱香小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.98,0:11:18.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.03,0:11:20.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么  停课吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.15,0:11:24.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  迟到了  就翘了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.99,0:11:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那去下路研吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.12,0:11:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,偶尔也想跟多聊聊祐太
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.87,0:11:30.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.96,0:11:31.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.62,0:11:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是算了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.29,0:11:36.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天晚上的班时间比较长
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.00,0:11:38.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回去小睡一下
